ZH: 这个公司不能仅仅通过提高产品价格来转嫁成本。
EN: This company cannot simply pass on costs by raising product prices.

ZH: 他们试图将责任转嫁给其他人。
EN: They are trying to shift the blame onto someone else.

ZH: 这次失败的计划导致了紧急的转嫁。
EN: The failed plan resulted in an urgent transfer of responsibilities.

ZH: 我们不能把所有责任都转嫁给那个员工。
EN: We cannot transfer all the responsibilities onto that employee.

